<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.7.4">
<l>kōvintaṉ kuṭakkūttaṉ kōvalaṉeṉ ṟeṉṟēkuṉittut</l>
<l>tēvun taṉṉaiyum pāṭiyāṭat tiruttiyeṉ ṉaikkoṇṭeṉ</l>
<l>pāvan taṉṉaiyum pāṟakkait temarē ḻeḻupiṟappu</l>
<l>mēvun taṉmaiya mākkiṉāṉ vallaṉem pirāṉviṭṭuvē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When [I] kept [and] saying “Govinda, pot dancer, cowherd”, bending,</l>
<l>singing the god [and] dancing, he perfected [and] took me,</l>
<l>discarding my sins so that they were scattered, [and] made me of [his] nature that will be attached</l>
<l>to our people through seven [times] seven births, the strong one, our lord, Viṣṇu.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
